Bajar opencv

Instalar cmake y cmake-qt-gui

Descomprimir opencv

Seguir estos pasos: (sacados de http://www.raben.com/book/export/html/9)
    * cd a la carpeta descomprimida
    * mkdir build && cd build
    * cmake -D CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -D BUILD_NEW_PYTHON_SUPPORT=ON -D INSTALL_PYTHON_EXAMPLES=ON -D INSTALL_C_EXAMPLES=ON -D BUILD_EXAMPLES=ON -D WITH_OPENGL=ON ..
    * make -j 2
    
